  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Climbing the stairs live on the recording took more courage than Coco expected; her legs felt a little weak at first.",
      "zh": "錄音時直接爬樓梯，比 Coco 想像中還需要勇氣，一開始她的腿還有點軟。"
    },
    {
      "en": "By the top step, though, her voice sounded brave and strong, not weak at all.",
      "zh": "但到了最上面一階，她的聲音聽起來很勇敢、很堅定，一點也不軟弱。"
    },
    {
      "en": "On Friday, the new episode began with footsteps instead of words.",
      "zh": "星期五，新的一集用腳步聲代替開場白開始。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Coco held the microphone close as she climbed, one step at a time. \"One. Two. Three.\"",
      "zh": "Coco 邊爬邊把麥克風拿近身邊：「一，二，三。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice spoke from a few steps behind. \"For fourteen years, almost nobody has done this.\"",
      "zh": "Bernice 從後面幾階跟著說：「十四年來，幾乎沒有人做過這件事。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"Fourteen years ago, one step here was damaged,\" Coco said. \"It was fixed within a week.\"",
      "zh": "Coco 說：「十四年前，這裡有一階壞了，一個星期內就修好了。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"But the story stayed broken for much longer than the step ever was.\"",
      "zh": "「但這個故事壞掉的時間，比那個階梯本身還要長得多。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "By the tenth step, her voice was calm. By the fourteenth, she was standing at the top, smiling.",
      "zh": "走到第十階時，她的聲音已經很平靜了，走到第十四階時，她已經站在最上面，笑著。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"Fourteen steps,\" she said. \"Completely normal. Completely safe.\"",
      "zh": "她說：「十四階，完全正常，完全安全。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "When the episode played in class, a few students laughed quietly.",
      "zh": "這一集在班上播放的時候，有幾個學生小聲地笑了。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"I've avoided those stairs since I was twelve,\" one student admitted. \"I don't even know why anymore.\"",
      "zh": "一個學生坦承：「我從十二歲就開始躲那座樓梯，連自己都不知道為什麼了。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "By lunchtime, three students had already walked up the fourth floor stairs, just to see for themselves.",
      "zh": "到了午餐時間，已經有三個學生特地走了一次四樓樓梯，只為了親自確認。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Mr. Pan watched all this from his desk and said nothing, but he looked happy about it.",
      "zh": "潘老師從他的桌子那邊看著這一切，什麼都沒說，但看起來很開心。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"Three cases were about something true that people forgot,\" he said later. \"This one was about something false that people remembered too well.\"",
      "zh": "他後來說：「前三個案子，都是關於一件被大家遺忘的真相，這一個，是關於一個被大家記得太清楚的假話。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "Coco wrote his sentence down, then added her own line underneath it.",
      "zh": "Coco 把他這句話寫下來，又在底下加了自己的一句話。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"Maybe every story in this school is either a truth someone forgot, or a fear someone never checked.\"",
      "zh": "「也許這間學校裡的每個故事，不是一個被遺忘的真相，就是一個從來沒有人去查證的害怕。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice read the line over her shoulder and laughed softly.",
      "zh": "Bernice 從她肩膀後面看到這句話，輕輕笑了。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"That's a big sentence for a Friday afternoon,\" she said.",
      "zh": "她說：「星期五下午講這麼大的一句話，有點嚴肅耶。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"Maybe,\" Coco said. \"But I think it's true.\"",
      "zh": "Coco 說：「也許吧，但我覺得是真的。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "That evening, the Friday Box was almost empty, just one small piece of paper at the bottom.",
      "zh": "那天傍晚，星期五箱子裡幾乎是空的，只有底部一張小紙片。"
    },
    {
      "en": "It was not a question this time, not even a full sentence. Just three words: \"Room 306. Listen.\"",
      "zh": "這次不是問題，甚至不是一個完整的句子，只有三個字：「306教室，聽。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice looked at Coco. \"Well,\" she said, \"that's new.\"",
      "zh": "Bernice 看著 Coco：「嗯，」她說：「這個倒是新鮮。」"
    },
    {
      "en": "Coco folded the paper carefully and put it in her notebook, right next to the growing list of Friday Box cases.",
      "zh": "Coco 小心地把紙折好，放進筆記本裡，就放在越來越長的 Friday Box 案件清單旁邊。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Whatever was waiting in Room 306, they both knew one thing for certain: they were not going to walk away from it.",
      "zh": "不管306教室裡藏著什麼，他們兩個都很確定一件事：他們不會轉身走開。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A few students admitted they used to be so afraid of the stairs that they would walk the long way around, even in bad weather.",
      "zh": "有幾個學生承認，他們以前太害怕那座樓梯，就算天氣不好也會繞遠路走。"
    },
    {
      "en": "\"I once ran the whole way around in the rain just to avoid it,\" one boy said, a little embarrassed.",
      "zh": "一個男生有點不好意思地說：「我甚至曾經冒雨繞了一大圈，就為了不走那座樓梯。」"
    }
  ],
